OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Political
OL,7,FCorrespondent Lise McNally takes a
OL,8,Flook back at Andy Burnham's career
OL,10,FJust three-and-a-half weeks after Andy
OL,11,FBurnham officially became
OL,12,FWestminster's newest MP he has been
OL,13,Funanimously crowned the Labour Party's
OL,14,Fnewest leader - and will become prime
OL,15,Fminister.
OL,17,FBut the Makerfield MP is far from a
OL,18,Fnewbie to national politics -
OL,19,Fespecially to the leadership race.
OL,26,@oD@Prt
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/19
