OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor defeated
OL,7,FReform UK's Robert Kenyon by 9,231
OL,8,Fvotes, up from 5,399 in 2024, and
OL,9,FLabour's vote share increased by
OL,10,F9.61%, on 18 June.
OL,12,FOver the past two decades the "King of
OL,13,Fthe North" has climbed the political
OL,14,Fladder in Parliament, held ministerial
OL,15,Froles in four government departments
OL,16,Fand run for Labour leadership twice.
OL,26,@tD@_OUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
