PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FAll before resigning and returning his
OL,7,Fattention to the North where he served
OL,8,Fas Greater Manchester Mayor from 2017
OL,9,Funtil he was elected back to
OL,10,Fparliament in 2026.
OL,12,FBurnham used his victory in the
OL,13,FMakerfield by-election as a
OL,14,Fspringboard to challenge for the
OL,15,FLabour leadership after Sir Keir
OL,16,FStarmer resigned - and with it, gain
OL,17,Fthe keys to No 10.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
