OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer set out a timetable
OL,7,Ffor his departure as prime minister
OL,8,Fjust three days after Burnham's
OL,9,Fvictory - stating he had asked
OL,10,F"whether I am best placed to lead us
OL,11,Finto the next general election?" -
OL,12,Fwith the answer given by the
OL,13,Fparliamentary party leading him to
OL,14,F"resign as leader of the Labour Party".
OL,16,FAfter 349 of the party's MPs nominated
OL,17,FBurnham it became impossible for any
OL,18,Fother candidate to gain the 81
OL,19,Fendorsements needed to challenge for
OL,20,Fthe Labour leadership.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
