PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FIt means it is third time lucky for
OL,7,FBurnham, after failing in two previous
OL,8,Fattempts to lead his party after being
OL,9,Fbeaten by Ed Miliband in 2010 and
OL,10,FJeremy Corbyn five years later.
OL,12,FLife before politics
OL,14,FAndy was born in Liverpool in 1970,
OL,15,Fhis father Kenneth was a BT engineer
OL,16,Fand his mother Eileen, a GP
OL,17,Freceptionist. He was one of three boys
OL,18,Fin a busy, Labour supporting
OL,19,Fhousehold, it was here that he
OL,20,Fdeveloped an interest in politics.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FHe went to school at a local Roman
OL,7,FCatholic comprehensive and later went
OL,8,Fon to study English at Cambridge, he
OL,9,Fwas the second in his family, after
OL,10,Fhis eldest brother, to go to
OL,11,Funiversity.
OL,13,FAfter graduating he took to
OL,14,Fjournalism, working for trade
OL,15,Fmagazines but in his early 20's he got
OL,16,Fhis first political gig as a
OL,17,Fresearcher for Tessa Jowell, then MP
OL,18,Ffor Dulwich and West Norwood.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
