PN,36408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FIt was during his tenure as Culture
OL,7,FSecretary, that he kickstarted the
OL,8,Froad to a second Hillsborough inquiry.
OL,10,FDuring a speech at the 20th
OL,11,FAnniversary Memorial Service at
OL,12,FAnfield, he was heckled, booed and met
OL,13,Fwith chants for justice for those who
OL,14,Flost their lives in the fatal crush at
OL,15,FHillsborough stadium.
OL,17,FAfter the memorial he took the issue
OL,18,Fto Downing Street and persuaded Gordon
OL,19,FBrown to bypass secrecy laws and
OL,20,Frelease all official documents
OL,21,Frelating to the crush.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThis paved the way for the formation
OL,7,Fof the Hillsborough Independent Panel,
OL,8,Fwhich would expose state corruption
OL,9,Fand a cover up by police to deflect
OL,10,Fblame onto Liverpool fans.
OL,12,FThe findings forced, then prime
OL,13,Fminister David Cameron, to issue a
OL,14,Fformal apology in the Commons and
OL,15,Fsuccessfully led to the 1991 inquest
OL,16,Fverdict of 'accidental death' being
OL,17,Fcompletely quashed.
OL,19,FIn 2016 a fresh inquest finally
OL,20,Fdeclared the 97 fans unlawfully killed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
