OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FLeadership elections
OL,8,FThe former Greater Manchester Mayor is
OL,9,Fan old hand at leadership contests
OL,10,Ftoo, having ran twice for the role
OL,11,Fmore than 10 years ago.
OL,13,FAfter Gordon Brown's resignation, in
OL,14,F2010 Burnham made his first bid for
OL,15,Fthe big job but was eliminated early
OL,16,Fon, finishing fourth out of five
OL,17,Fcandidates.
OL,19,FEd Miliband ultimately won, but
OL,20,FBurnham spent the next five years
OL,21,Fbuilding up his appeal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
