PN,36411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FIn 2015, he tried again entering the
OL,7,Frace as the bookies favourite but was
OL,8,Fit wasn't to be, with Jeremy Corbyn
OL,9,Fwinning by a 59.5% landslide.
OL,11,FHe remained in Westminster for another
OL,12,Fyear as Shadow Home Secretary under
OL,13,FCorbyn.
OL,15,FServing in the shadow cabinet led to
OL,16,Fan often-heard criticism within Labour
OL,17,Franks ` that Burnham, having supported
OL,18,Fboth Corbyn and New Labour, is a
OL,19,Fweather vane who goes with the flow to
OL,20,Fensure his own electoral success.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
