PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FIn 2017, amid persistent Labour
OL,7,Finfighting, he left Westminster and
OL,8,Ftook more than 60% of the vote to
OL,9,Fbecome the first metro mayor of
OL,10,FGreater Manchester.
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Mayor
OL,14,FDuring his first working week in
OL,15,Foffice, he outlined plans to end rough
OL,16,Fsleeping in the region by 2020 and
OL,17,Fannounced he would donate 15% of his
OL,18,F#110,000 salary, on a monthly basis,
OL,19,Fto kick-start a homelessness fund that
OL,20,Fwould support frontline projects.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThe 2020 target was not met, but he
OL,7,Fhas continued to work on reducing
OL,8,Fhomelessness in the region.
OL,10,FHis popularity hit a new peak during
OL,11,Fthe covid pandemic when he publicly
OL,12,Ftook on Boris Johnson over the
OL,13,Fdecision to put Greater Manchester
OL,14,Finto the highest level of lockdown
OL,15,Frestrictions.
OL,17,FA huge point of contention was the
OL,18,Flack of financial support for low paid
OL,19,Fworkers, the stand-off earned him the
OL,20,Fnickname, 'King of the North'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
