OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThe 56-year-old has also earned
OL,7,Frespect through his handling of two
OL,8,Fterror attacks during his mayoralty:
OL,9,FManchester Arena was targeted in a
OL,10,Fsuicide bombing just weeks after he
OL,11,Fstarted in 2017 and Heaton Park
OL,12,Fsynagogue was attacked in October 2025.
OL,14,FAnother success for Burnham was the
OL,15,Fintegration of Greater Manchester's
OL,16,Ftransport system to form 'The Bee
OL,17,FNetwork'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
