CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FThis made Greater Manchester the first
OL,7,Fplace outside of London to bring bus
OL,8,Fservices and other modes of transport
OL,9,Ftogether and back under public control.
OL,11,FIt appeared to contribute to another
OL,12,Flandslide election victory when he won
OL,13,Fa third term in 2024 with 63.4% of the
OL,14,Fvote.
OL,16,FReturn to Parliament
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
