OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FIn January, he positioned himself for
OL,7,Fa potential return to Parliament by
OL,8,Fapplying to Labour's national
OL,9,Fexecutive committee (NEC), saying: "I
OL,10,Fhave learnt in my nine years as mayor
OL,11,Fthat Manchester won't be able to be
OL,12,Feverything it should be without
OL,13,Fsimilar changes at a national level.
OL,15,F"This is why I feel the need to go
OL,16,Fback."
OL,18,FBut that attempt to win a route back
OL,19,Fin the Gorton and Denton by-election
OL,20,Fwas blocked by the NEC, deepening the
OL,21,Fdivision between himself and Sir Keir.
OL,26,@qD@dOUwD@AOUxD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36417
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FBy the time Josh Simons quit his
OL,7,FMakerfield seat to give Burnham
OL,8,Fanother opportunity to return, Sir
OL,9,FKeir's authority was so diminished
OL,10,Fafter May's local and devolved
OL,11,Felections that he could not block his
OL,12,Fwould-be challenger from the ballot
OL,13,Fpaper.
OL,15,FWhat's next?
OL,17,FAfter Starmer's resignation cleared
OL,18,Fthe way for Burnham's bid to become
OL,19,Fthe UK's seventh PM in a decade the MP
OL,20,Fsaid he would not call a general
OL,21,Felection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,365,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36418
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784566088
OL,3,CWho is Andy Burnham and what led him
OL,4,Cto return to Westminster?
OL,6,FBut he revealed he would seek to
OL,7,Fpersuade Labour to put voting reform
OL,8,Fin its next manifesto.
OL,10,FBurnham is under no legal obligation
OL,11,Fto call a general election before the
OL,12,Fscheduled end of Parliament in 2029,
OL,13,Fthough a prime minister can choose to
OL,14,Fdo so at any point before then.
OL,16,FIt is the first time there has been a
OL,17,Fdirect challenge to the leader of the
OL,18,FLabour Party while they are prime
OL,19,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/19
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
